Detailed Description

Holds the results of a successful match of a regular expression against a given string.

Only used internally, thus sparsely documented (though the defining public interface has full documentation).

See also:
java.util.regex.MatchResult

int32_t* gaia::webkit::MatchResultImpl::mpoffsets [private]

Holds the offsets of the groups in the input text.

The first two elements specifiy start and end of the zero group, the next two specify group 1, and so on.
